{"tid":1113037,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"雷朋三世作者 Monkey Punch 逝世　享年 83 歲","createTime":"2019-04-17T17:49:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-18T02:33:06.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"518d6e37d42a1d14fa4aade6919eb4d424c850bf","tid":1113037,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:49:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/3-04_HtOfK_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F3-04_HtOfK_1200x0.png&h=7acc2246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n日本經典漫畫《雷朋三世》的作者，原名加藤一彥的 Monkey Punch 逝世，享年 83 歲。官方網站公布，加藤一彥上星期四晚 7 時，因肺炎逝世。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/vcover_vt_pic/0/gjjamwzsawpahk41529382695/260\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fvcover_vt_pic%2F0%2Fgjjamwzsawpahk41529382695%2F260&h=0a3e0d7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\r\n<br />\r\n加藤一彥 1937 年在北海道出生，1967 年他開始連載他的代表作《雷朋三世》，這部作品歷年來陸續改編做動畫、遊戲、真人電影等，是膾炙人口的經典漫畫作品。漫畫主角雷朋三世，設定為法國作家莫理斯盧布朗筆下的俠盜亞森羅蘋的孫，是世界最著名的神偷，這部作品 1969 年已連載完，但後續作品和週邊商品至今仍有推出。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n加藤一彥作為日本殿堂級漫畫家，2005 年成為大阪大手前大學媒體與藝術學院漫畫動畫教授，2010 年出任東京工科大學客座教授。"},{"pid":"9b9d9f329f35f56ddbec934ddc31c1479437a044","tid":1113037,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T17:50:18.000Z","msg":"童年回憶, rip <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f47d424b4f79cfe8cf12f4549d6c0e1db97d0b77","tid":1113037,"uid":43041,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:15:13.000Z","msg":"篇報導邊個寫，又雷朋又羅蘋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亞森羅蘋港譯咪雷朋囉"},{"pid":"67ec4649a2ef1498c4f038dc888ee1eadfdd7ab3","tid":1113037,"uid":28913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f47d424b4f79cfe8cf12f4549d6c0e1db97d0b77","tid":1113037,"uid":43041,"lik